rty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"United Bermuda Party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Bermuda_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Bermuda_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 5860, \"end\": 5863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6283848200586072e-13, \"text\": \"PLP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The presence\", \"from\": 5760, \"to\": 5772}, {\"ngram\": \"their anti-Black stances\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5847}, {\"ngram\": \"the party's image\", \"from\": 5899, \"to\": 5916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This inclusion raises questions about the party's commitment to its original mission and its alignment with elitist and potentially White supremacist ideologies.\", \"from\": 5919, \"to\": 6080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6051, \"end\": 6068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_supremacy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"White supremacist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_supremacy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_supremacy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This inclusion\", \"from\": 5919, \"to\": 5933}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 5941, \"to\": 5950}, {\"ngram\": \"the party's commitment\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5979}, {\"ngram\": \"its original mission\", \"from\": 5983, \"to\": 6003}, {\"ngram\": \"its alignment\", \"from\": 6008, \"to\": 6021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The PLP's staunch opposition to LGBTQ+ rights, a stance widely recognised as a vestige of colonialism and White supremacy, highlights a troubling contradiction.\", \"from\": 6081, \"to\": 6241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6085, \"end\": 6088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6283848200586072e-13, \"text\": \"PLP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 6187, \"end\": 6202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_supremacy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"White supremacy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_supremacy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_supremacy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+ rights\", \"from\": 6113, \"to\": 6126}, {\"ngram\": \"a stance\", \"from\": 6128, \"to\": 6136}, {\"ngram\": \"a vestige\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6167}, {\"ngram\": \"colonialism\", \"from\": 6171, \"to\": 6182}, {\"ngram\": \"a troubling contradiction\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This homophobia, entrenched in the party's policies, undermines its claims of being pro-Black, pro-labour and progressive.\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This homophobia\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6257}, {\"ngram\": \"the party's policies\", \"from\": 6273, \"to\": 6293}, {\"ngram\": \"its claims\", \"from\": 6306, \"to\": 6316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With points alone, White supremacy seems to be a pervasive issue plaguing the PLP of today.\", \"from\": 6365, \"to\": 6456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6443, \"end\": 6446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6283848200586072e-13, \"text\": \"PLP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliamentary_Labour_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 6370, \"to\": 6376}, {\"ngram\": \"White supremacy\", \"from\": 6384, \"to\": 6399}, {\"ngram\": \"a pervasive issue\", \"from\": 6412, \"to\": 6429}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 645