\"from\": 6899, \"to\": 6913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bermuda's political landscape is characterised by a lack of genuine commitment to addressing systemic inequalities.\", \"from\": 6916, \"to\": 7031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6916, \"end\": 6923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3271187023748916e-18, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 6966, \"to\": 6972}, {\"ngram\": \"genuine commitment\", \"from\": 6976, \"to\": 6994}, {\"ngram\": \"systemic inequalities\", \"from\": 7009, \"to\": 7030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rhetoric of progress and inclusivity rings hollow when the actions of those in power perpetuate the very disparities they claim to oppose.\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rhetoric\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7044}, {\"ngram\": \"progress\", \"from\": 7048, \"to\": 7056}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity rings\", \"from\": 7061, \"to\": 7078}, {\"ngram\": \"the actions\", \"from\": 7091, \"to\": 7102}, {\"ngram\": \"power perpetuate\", \"from\": 7115, \"to\": 7131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is time for a reckoning, a thorough examination of our political institutions, and a genuine effort to bridge the gap between the two Bermudas.\", \"from\": 7175, \"to\": 7321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7312, \"end\": 7320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9965086078190798e-18, \"text\": \"Bermudas\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 7181, \"to\": 7185}, {\"ngram\": \"a reckoning\", \"from\": 7190, \"to\": 7201}, {\"ngram\": \"a thorough examination\", \"from\": 7203, \"to\": 7225}, {\"ngram\": \"our political institutions\", \"from\": 7229, \"to\": 7255}, {\"ngram\": \"a genuine effort\", \"from\": 7261, \"to\": 7277}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 7288, \"to\": 7295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The divide between public and private education in Bermuda is a microcosm of the larger issues of race and class that permeate our society.\", \"from\": 7323, \"to\": 7462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7374, \"end\": 7381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3271187023748916e-18, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The divide\", \"from\": 7323, \"to\": 7333}, {\"ngram\": \"public and private education\", \"from\": 7342, \"to\": 7370}, {\"ngram\": \"a microcosm\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7396}, {\"ngram\": \"the larger issues\", \"from\": 7400, \"to\": 7417}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 7421, \"to\": 7425}, {\"ngram\": \"class\", \"from\": 7430, \"to\": 7435}, {\"ngram\": \"our society\", \"from\": 7450, \"to\": 7461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is only through sustained and committed efforts that we can truly bridge the gap and ensure that every young person has the opportunity to thrive and represent our jurisdiction on the world stage.\", \"from\": 7463, \"to\": 7662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sustained and committed efforts\", \"from\": 7482, \"to\": 7513}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 7539, \"to\": 7546}, {\"ngram\": \"every young person\", \"from\": 7563, \"to\": 7581}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 7586, \"to\": 7601}, {\"ngram\": \"our jurisdiction\", \"from\": 7626, \"to\": 7642}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 7646, \"to\": 7661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The PLP government must reconcile its past with its present and realign with the principles it was founded upon to truly serve the people of Bermuda.\", \"from\": 7664, \"to\": 7813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7668, \"